Titolo: Armageddon Empires

Anno: 2007

Descrizione: Armageddon Empires is a 4x turn-based strategy video game for Microsoft Windows and Mac OS X.  It was released internationally for Microsoft Windows on July 16, 2007, and for Mac OS X on October 9, 2007.  The title is the first game released by independent game developer Cryptic Comet.